{
  "texts": [
    "However, this requires access to guaranteed and controlled knowledge.",
    "And this is not a given.",
    "For example, the xAI team 38 has already announced that its new Grok model has inadvertently learned too much from ChatGPT output posted on the internet 39.",
    "This shows another side of our new reality.",
    "In the future, experts may increasingly have to separate synthetic data from real data."
  ]
}